        {
          "type": "reasoning",
          "text": "The user is asking follow-up questions about OS resource management and pagefile. Let me answer their questions clearly, marking [ФАКТ / МНЕНИЕ] and confidence levels as per the protocol.\n\nThey're also reading Tanenbaum, so I should connect explanations to OS concepts they're learning.\n\nI'm in plan mode - I can only read/explain/plan, no edits. That's fine, we're just discussing concepts.",
