          "text": "The user has three specific questions that show they're genuinely trying to understand the concepts rather than just nodding along. This is good - I need to give clear, concrete explanations.\n\nLet me answer each one carefully.\n\n1. \"ОС переключает процессы?\" - They want to confirm: does the OS switch between processes?\n\n2. \"что ещё не выделено физически\" это вообще как? типа занято на будущее, но пока что там пусто? - They're confused about the distinction between virtual memory allocation and physical backing.\n\n3. \"а адресное пространство это вообще что?\" - They want a clear definition of address space.\n\nI need to keep it concrete, use analogies that work, and not praise them.",
